ntact%20the%20airline%20concerned%20for%20updated%20flight%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%2014%20trains%20in%20northern%20India%20was%20also%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20foggy%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT-III%20(Category%20III)%20Instrument%20Landing%20System%20(ILS)%20is%20an%20anti-fog%20landing%20system%20initiated%20by%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20to%20facilitate%20landings%20during%20low%20runway%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorning%20scenes%20from%20iconic%20locations%20such%20as%20India%20Gate%2C%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%2C%20AIIMS%2C%20Safdarjung%2C%20and%20Anand%20Vihar%20depicted%20a%20city%20shrouded%20in%20dense%20fog%2C%20drastically%20reducing%20visibility%20and%20prompting%20residents%20to%20seek%20refuge%20in%20night%20shelters%20as%20the%20cold%20wave%20intensified%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD's%20satellite%20images%20revealed%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20fog's%20reach%2C%20spanning%20across%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Moradabad%20and%20Kanpur%2C%20visibility%20plummeted%20to%20almost%20zero%2C%20causing%20disruptions%20to%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20prevailing%20conditions%2C%20people%20were%20observed%20gathering%20around%20bonfires%20along%20roads%20and%20lanes%20to%20combat%20the%20bone-chilling%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20also%20issued%20a%20warning%20about%20potential%20health%20impacts%20due%20to%20the%20dense%20fog%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20%26quot%3BDense%20fog%20contains%20particulate%20matter%20and%20other%20pollutants%2C%20and%20in%20case%20exposed%2C%20it%20gets%20lodged%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20clogging%20them%20and%20decreasing%20their%20functional%20capacity%2C%20which%20increases%20episodes%20of%20wheezing%2C%20coughing%2C%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703567520000%2C%22v