intelligence%20regarding%20the%20presence%20of%20terrorists%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt.%20Col.%20Natt%20was%20an%20experienced%20officer%20who%20had%20served%20in%20the%20army%20for%20almost%2020%20years.%20Before%20joining%20the%20Territorial%20Army%2C%20Lt.%20Col.%20Natt%20joined%20the%20regular%20army%20in%201997%20after%20passing%20out%20from%20the%20Officers%20Training%20Academy%20in%20Chennai%20and%20was%20commissioned%20in%20the%2019th%20Battalion%20of%20the%20Brigade%20of%20Guards%2C%20a%20mechanized%20infantry%20regiment%2C%20through%20the%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20entry%20of%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Lt%20Colonel%20Karanbir%20Singh%20Natt%2C%20Sena%20Medal%20(Gallantry)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Lt%20Colonel%20Karanbir%20Singh%20Natt%2C%20Sena%20Medal%20(Gallantry)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fg938th38_lt-colonel-kbs-natt-_625x300_26_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt%20Colonel%20Karanbir%20Singh%20Natt%2C%20Sena%20Medal%20(Gallantry)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20for%20over%20ten%20years%2C%20he%20left%20the%20regular%20army%2C%20though%20his%20love%20for%20the%20olive%20green%20never%20ended%20and%20he%20joined%20the%20Territorial%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENovember%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202015%2C%20the%20Kupwara%20area%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20witnessed%20back-to-back%20encounters.%20On%20November%2017%2C%20the%2041%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20commanded%20by%20Colonel%20Santosh%20Mahadik%20launched%20a%20massive%20anti-terror%20operation%20in%20the%20Kalaroos%20area%20of%20Kupwara.%20He%20led%20the%20operation%20from%20the%20front%20and%20in%20a%20fierce%20gun%20battle%2C%20he%20was%20hit%20in%20the%20chest%20and%20was%20severely%20injured%20but%20died%20due%20to%20the%20gunshot%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt.%20Colonel%20Natt%20received%20a%20burst%20of%20fire%20after%20the%20terrorists%20were%20cornered%20in%20a%20hut.%20The%20officer%20was%20hit%20in%20the%20face%20by%20a%20Kalashnikov%20bullet%20and%20was%20seriously%20injured%20but%20he%20saved%20three%20of%20his%20men%20during%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Long%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1583884880%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0DzwHg5JJyE3ATVkuRBAoX95QwSgh1MbS5jdovrPbPTAdKokeJ7HQALnA5upxFmNdl%2F%3Fapp%3Dfbl%5C%22%3EColonel%20Anil%20Alagh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Retired)%2C%20who%20was%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20Lt.%20Colonel%20Natt's%20former%20regiment%2C%20wrote%20a%20heartfelt%20post%20in%202018%20to%20share%20the%20struggle%20of%20Lt.%20Col.%20Natt's%20family%20and%20what%20he%20is%20going%20through.%20The%20officer%20was%20airlifted%20to%20Srinagar%20and%20then%20taken%20to%20the%20Army's%20Research%20and%20Referral%20hospital%20in%20Delhi.%20Lt.%20Col.%20Natt%20was%20in%20a%20vegetative%20state%2C%20a%20condition%20in%20which%20a%20person%20was%20awake%20but%20shows%20no%20sign%20of%20awareness%2C%20on%20the%20day%20he%20was%20brought%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20battle%20for%20the%20infantry%20officer%20and%20his%20family%20began.%20He%20slipped%20into%20a%20coma%20due%20to%20the%20injuries.%20Col.%20Alagh%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20post%20on%20Lt.%20Col.%20Natt's%20wife%2C%20Navreet's%20request%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20wife%2C%20children%20Guneet%20and%20Ashmeet%2C%20his%20parents%20and%20other%20veterans%20were%20by%20his%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20find%20the%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Col.%20Alagh.%20%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20rips%20apart%20every%20time%20Ashi%20says%2C%20'When%20will%20Papa%20get%20up%3F%20When%20will%20he%20come%20to%20pick%20me%20up%20from%20school%3F%20When%20will%20he%20see%20my%20school%20functions%3F'%20Many%20more%20questions...I%20hug%20her%20tightly%20and%20say%2C%20'Very%20soon.'%20Wondering%20what%20will%20happen%3