A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsydney-sweeney-felt-so-good-in-rolling-stones-music-video-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jailed%20Putin%20Critic%20%26quot%3BFound%26quot%3B%20In%20Arctic%20Penal%20Colony%202%20Weeks%20After%20He%20Vanished%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJailed%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%20Alexei%20Navalny%20has%20been%20moved%20to%20a%20penal%20colony%20in%20the%20Arctic%2C%20allies%20said%20on%20Monday%20after%20over%20two%20weeks%20during%20which%20his%20whereabouts%20were%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20transferred%20Russia's%20most%20prominent%20opposition%20politician%20to%20an%20isolated%20penal%20colony%20three%20months%20before%20a%20presidential%20vote%20expected%20to%20easily%20hand%20Vladimir%20Putin%20a%20fifth%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20found%20Alexei%20Navalny%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20ally%2C%20Kira%20Yarmysh%2C%20said%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20now%20in%20IK-3%20in%20the%20settlement%20of%20Kharp%20in%20the%20Yamalo-Nenets%20Autonomous%20District%2C%26quot%3B%20Yarmysh%20added.%20%26quot%3BHis%20lawyer%20visited%20him%20today.%20Alexei%20is%20doing%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20of%20Kharp%2C%20home%20to%20about%205%2C000%20people%2C%20is%20located%20above%20the%20Arctic%20Circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20northern%20and%20remote%20colonies%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Ivan%20Zhdanov%2C%20who%20manages%20Navalny's%20Anti-Corruption%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConditions%20there%20are%20harsh%2C%20with%20a%20special%20regime%20in%20the%20permafrost%20zone%26quot%3B%20and%20very%20little%20contact%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20Zhdanov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20welcomed%20reports%20that%20the%20dissident%20was%20finally%20located%20alive%20but%20slammed%20Moscow%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20targeting%20of%20Navalny%20and%20the%20more%20than%20600%20other%20political%20prisoners%20Russia%20has%20imprisoned%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20said%20it%20remained%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%20for%20Mr.%20Navalny's%20wellbeing%20and%20the%20conditions%20of%20his%20unjust%20detention%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20it%20joined%20Navalny's%20family%20and%20supporters%20%26quot%3Bin%20calling%20for%20his%20immediate%20release%2C%20without%20conditions%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20Russia%20to%20%26quot%3Bend%20its%20escalating%20repression%20of%20independent%20voices%20in%20Russia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20condemned%20the%20transfer%2C%20with%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20spokeswoman%20saying%20Russia%20had%20committed%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Isolate%20Alexei'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20mobilised%20huge%20anti-government%20protests%20before%20being%20jailed%20in%202021%2C%20after%20surviving%20an%20attempt%20to%20assassinate%20him%20by%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20detention%20at%20the%20IK-6%20penal%20colony%2C%20some%20250%20kilometres%20(155%20miles)%20east%20of%20Moscow%20in%20the%20Vladimir%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20extended%20his%20sentence%20to%2019%20years%20on%20extremism%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20ruled%20he%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20harsher%20special%20regime%20prison%2C%20usually%20housing%20particularly%20dangerous%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20weeks%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20Navalny%20was%20found%20at%20IK-3%20--%20%26quot%3BPolar%20Wolf%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20strict-regime%20colony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20nearby%20penal%20colony%20No.18%20--%20%26quot%3BPolar%20Owl%26quot%3B%20--%20which%20has%20an%20even%20harsher%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20for%20transfers%20to%20take%20weeks%20in%20Russia%2C%20as%20prisoners%20are%20slowly%20moved%20by%20rail%20between%20far-flung%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20complete%20lack%20of%20news%20on%20his%20whereabouts%20had%20spurred%20concerns%20from%20allies%2C%20rights%20groups%20and%20Western%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20allies%20said%20they%20had%20sent%20requests%20to%20over%20600%20detention%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20complete%20ban%20of%20information%20about%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhdanov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllies%20believe%20the%20Kremlin%20aimed%20to%20further%20isolate%20the%20vocal%20critic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20authorities%20wanted%20to%20isolate%20Alexei%2C%20especially%20before%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhdanov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20will%20hold%20a%20presidential%20vote%20in%20March%202024%2C%20with%20Putin%20the%20undisputed%20favourite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Kremlin-friendly%20parties%20are%20due%20to%20put%20forward%20candidates%20for%20the%20vote%2C%20but%20the%20real%20opposition%20has%20been%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20has%20for%20years%20weakened%20Russia's%20independent%20politicians%20and%20activists%2C%20a%20clampdown%20that%20accelerated%20after%20the%20Kremlin%20ordered%20Russian%20troops%20into%20Ukraine%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20movement%20in%20particular%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20Kremlin%20repression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20offensive%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Navalny's%20organisation%20was%20declared%20extremist%2C%20which%20facilitated%20the%20prosecution%20of%20members%20and%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20regional%20heads%20of%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Foundation%20were%20jailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20was%20Lilia%20Chanysheva%2C%20Navalny's%20ally%20in%20the%20central%20Bashkortostan%20Republic%2C%20who%20was%20handed%20seven%20and%20a%20h