0for%20The%20Chiefs'%20underperformance%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20trending%20'Taylor%20Swift%20curse'%20theory.%20Fans%20link%20her%20presence%20at%20the%20games%20to%20the%20team's%20poor%20performance%20and%20even%20blame%20her%20for%20Travis%20Kelce's%20injury.%20Swifties%20defend%20her%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20she's%20there%20to%20support%20her%20boyfriend%20and%20that%20the%20team's%20performance%20is%20not%20her%20fault.%20Indian%20Swifties%20draw%20a%20parallel%20with%20Bollywood%20actress%20Anushka%20Sharma%2C%20who%20faces%20similar%20trolling%20when%20her%20husband%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20underperforms%20on%20the%20cricket%20field.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vacancies%2C%20Representation%20and%20Toilets%3A%20What%20Ails%20India's%20Judiciary%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26092503%2F27905720280_4def8d5561_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20judiciary%20has%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20pendency.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20to%20find%20pretrial%20detainees%20having%20to%20wait%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20to%20just%20have%20their%20cases%20heard%20before%20a%20trial%20court%20or%20a%20senior%20citizen%20fighting%20a%20property%20dispute%20for%2030%20or%2040%20years%20in%20a%20civil%20court.%20These%20agonising%20delays%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20a%20series%20of%20reasons.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Research%20and%20Planning%2C%20in%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20report%2C%20has%20looked%20at%20some%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20ones%20among%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98State%20of%20the%20Judiciary%2C%E2%80%99%20closely%20looks%20at%20issues%20of%20vacancy%2C%20lack%20of%20diversity%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20lack%20of%20infrastructure%20for%20both%20judges%20and%20litigants%2C%20and%20the%20sub-optimal%20working%20conditions%20of%20court%20staff%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20on%20October%202023%2C%20the%20report%20points%20out%20that%20there%20are%20over%20five%20crore%20pending%20cases%20across%20all%20higher%20and%20subordinate%20courts%20in%20India.%20To%20handle%20them%2C%20however%2C%20there%20are%20only%2020%2C580%20judges%20working%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20high%20courts%20and%20district%20courts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20(as%20on%20October%201%2C%202023)%20reveals%20that%20as%20against%20the%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%201%2C114%20judges%20in%20the%20high%20courts%20across%20the%20country%2C%20as%20many%20as%20347%20positions%20are%20vacant.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20district%20judiciary%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2025%2C081%20judges%2C%20as%20of%20April%202023%2C%20the%20working%20strength%20was%20only%2019%2C781.%20As%20many%20as%205%2C300%20district%20judges%E2%80%99%20positions%20are%20vacant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20been%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20clear%20this%20mounting%20pendency%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20several%20methods%20to%20compute%20the%20requisite%20strength%20of%20judges%20in%20the%20district%20judiciary%20has%20been%20formulated.%20In%201987%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20in%20its%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98Manpower%20Planning%20in%20Judiciary%3A%20A%20Blueprint%E2%80%99%20recommended%20the%20use%20of%20the%20ratio%20of%20judges%E2%80%99%20strength%20per%20million%20population%20as%20the%20criterion%20to%20plan%20the%20judicial%20staffing.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20stated%20that%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20legislative%20representation%20can%20be%20worked%20out%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20earlier%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20population%20and%20if%20other%20services%20of%20the%20State%20%E2%80%93%20bureaucracy%2C%20police%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20can%20also%20be%20similarly%20planned%2C%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20at%20all%20for%20the%20non-extension%20of%20this%20principle%20to%20the%20judicial%20services.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demographic%20method%2C%20which%20is%20a%20most%20common%20method%2C%20suggested%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20ratio%20of%2010%20judges%20per%20million%20people%20to%2050%20judges%20per%20million%20people.%20This%20was%20endorsed%20later%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20in%202002%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F61639974%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520Court%2520in%2520All%2520India%2Cassist%2520in%2520implementing%2520their%2520decisions.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20India%20Judges%20Association%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20in%202014%2C%20suggested%20the%20Disposal%20Method.%20It%20recommended%20that%20the%20total%20number%20of%20judges%20required%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20pendency%20can%20be%20calculated%20by%20computing%20the%20number%20of%20judges%20required%20to%20clear%20the%20existing%20backlog%20and%20the%20new%20filings%20of%20cases%2C%20based%20on%20the%20average%20disposal%20of%20cases%20per%20judge.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20time%20to%20time%2C%20newer%20suggestions%20to%20overcome%20pendency%20have%20been%20given%20by%20different%20committees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20date%20of%20notification%20of%20number%20of%20vacancies%20by%20the%20high%20court%20to%20the%20actual%20date%20of%20joining%2C%20the%20process%20%E2%80%93%20as%20prescribed%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EMalik%20Mazhar%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0judgment%20%E2%80%93%20should%20take%20about%20273%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20study%2C%20however%2C%20has%20found%20that%20only%20nine%20states%20adhere%20to%20the%20timeline.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBihar%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20took%20945%20days%20to%20complete%20the%20last%20recruitment%20process%20of%20Civil%20Judge%20(Junior%20Division)%2C%20computed%20from%20the%20date%20of%20advertisement%20(March%209%2C%202020)%20to%20the%20date%20of%20final%20result%20(October%2010%2C%202022).%20This%20delay%2C%20the%20high%20court%20of%20Patna%20attributed%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20But%20the%20report%20points%20to%20similar%20delay%20even%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20recruitment%20process%20of%202018-19%20in%20Bihar%20took%20463%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20report%20has%20identified%20litigation%20(candidates%20challenging%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20examination)%20and%20different%20recruitment%20authority%20as%20the%20primary%20cause%20for%20the%20delay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInclusivity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20pluralistic%20democracy%20like%20India%2C%20where%20there%20is%20vast%20social%2C%20geographical%20and%20religious%20diversity%2C%20a%20representative%20and%20inclusive%20judiciary%20is%20imperative%20to%20repose%20faith%20in%20the%20public%20in%20the%20justice%20system.%20The%20report%20analyses%20the%20representation%20of%20female%20judges%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20high%20court%20and%20district%20courts.%20Alongside%20gender%2C%20the%20report%20also%20examines%20the%20representation%20of%20those%20from%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20in%20the%20district%20judiciary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Harassment%E2%80%99%2C%20Pleas%20and%20a%20Petition%20Dismissed%20in%208%20Seconds%3A%20Behind%20Woman%20Civil%20Judge%E2%80%99s%20Letter%20to%20CJI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20there%20are%20no%20provisions%20for%20reservation%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%2C%20class%20or%20gender%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20high%20courts%20(which%20are%20made%20under%20Articles%20124%20and%20217%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20respectively)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%20has%20clearly%20laid%20down%20%E2%80%98diversity%E2%80%99%20as%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20to%20consider%20in%20appointing%20judges%20to%20the%20apex%20court.%20The%20diversity%20consideration%20in%20itself%20has%20not%20yielded%20the%20desired%20result%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20are%20some%20important%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20highest%20court%20presently%20has%20only%20three%20female%20judges%20(9.3%25)%20out%20of%20its%20working%20strength%20of%2032%20judges%2C%20as%20of%20October%201%2C%202023.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20situation%20is%20just%20as%20grim%20in%20the%20high%20courts.%20Out%20of%20767%20permanent%20and%20additional%20judges%20in%20the%20high%20courts%20across%20India%2C%20only%20103%20are%20female%20judges%20(i.e%2013.42%25).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20district%20judiciary%2C%20however%2C%20shows%20considerable%20improvement%20with%20the%20strength%20of%2036.33%25%20female%20judges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20judicial%20officers%20in%20the%20district%20judiciary%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20state%20governments%20and%20respective%20high%20courts.%20The%20report%20has%20found%20that%20states%20like%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20provide%20reservations%20for%20women%20in%20judicial%20examinations%20to%20promote%20gender%20diversity.%20As%20many%20as%2014%20states%20(of%20the%2016%20examined%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20report)%20have%20appointed%20more%20than%2050%25%20female%20judicial%20officers%20in%20the%20last%20civil%20judges%20(junior%20division)%20recruitment%20examination.%20While%20Sikkim%20selected%2080%25%20female%20officers%2C%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%2065%25%20and%2063.6%25%20respectively%2C%20female%20judicial%20officers%20were%20selected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20lack%20of%20adequate%20gender%20representation%20in%20judiciary%20that%20the%20states%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20but%20also%20the%20complete%20disregard%20shown%20towards%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20existing%20female%20judicial%20officers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToilets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20instance%20that%20the%20report%20looks%20at%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20female-%20friendly%20toilets%20in%20the%20Indian%20courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20says%20a%20mere%206.7%25%20of%20toilets%20facilities%20in%20courts%20across%20India%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfemale-%20friendly%E2%80%9D%20with%20provisions%20like%20sanitary%20napkin-vending%20machines%20set%20up%20in%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20in%20the%20high%20courts%2C%20the%20report%20has%20found%2C%20the%20number%20of%20washrooms%20is%20adequate%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20current%20strength%20of%20judges.%20This%20count%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20increased%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20sanctioned%20strength.%20The%20real%20concern%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20lower%20judiciary.%20The%20report%2C%20terming%20the%20condition%20of%20toilets%20in%20the%20lower%20courts%20%E2%80%9Cdeplorable%E2%80%9D%2C%20states%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20ground%20reality%20that%20court%20complexes%20at%20the%20district%20level%20not%20only%20have%20inadequate%20washrooms%20but%20at%20times%2C%20have%20washrooms%20that%20are%20dysfunctional%2C%20with%20broken%20doors%20and%20do%20not%20have%20regular%20supply%20of%20running%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20As%20many%20as%2012%20high%20courts%20submitted%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstark%20inadequacy%E2%80%9D%20of%20toilets%20for%20judges%2C%20staff%2C%20lawyers%20and%20litigants%20in%20the%20district%20judiciary.%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20too%20had%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20lack%20of%20proper%20toilets%20in%20court%20rooms%20in%20one%20of%20his%20recent%20speeches.%20The%20report%20also%20pointed%20at%20the%20need%20to%20build%20toilets%20bearing%20in%20mind%20the%20need%20to%20also%20accommodate%20the%20transgender%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20to%20study%20the%20caste%20diversity%20in%20the%20lower%20judiciary%2C%20the%20report%20looks%20at%20six%20states%20namely%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIn%20these%20states%2C%20out%20of%201%2C389%20seats%20advertised%20for%20the%20Civil%20Judge%20(Junior%20Division)%20exam%20recently%2C%20766%20posts%20were%20advertised%20for%20the%20reserved%20category%2C%20which%20includes%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Economically%20Weaker%20Section%20(EWS)%2C%20and%20others%2C%20as%20applicable%20to%20each%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmore-than-three-in-four-high-court-judges-appointed-since-2018-upper-caste-law-ministry%5C%22%3EMore%20Than%20Three%20in%20Four%20High%20Court%20Judges%20Appointed%20Since%202018%20Upper-Caste%3A%20Law%20Ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20has%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20six%20states%20examined%2C%2037.5%25%20seats%20of%20the%20posts%20advertised%20for%20the%20reserved%20category%20remained%20unfilled.%20These%20unfilled%20vacancies%20contribute%20to%2066.3%25%20of%20the%20overall%20seats%20that%20remained%20unfilled%20in%20the%20last%20recruitment%20exam%20of%20the%20Civil%20Judge%20(junior%20Division).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20important%20data%20point%20that%20the%20report%20has%20thrown%20light%20on%20is%20the%20caste%20breakup%20of%20the%20recent%20recruitments%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20high%20courts.%20As%20many%20as%20492%20out%20of%20the%20650%20judges%20appointed%20between%202018%20to%202023%20belong%20to%20the%20General%20Category%2C%20the%20report%20reveals.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20judiciary%20needs%20maximum%20judge%20strength%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20mounting%20arrears%2C%20unfilled%20vacancies%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20reserved%20category%2C%20calls%20for%20sincere%20action.%20It%20is%20a%20positive%20obligation%20upon%20the%20state%20to%20take%20affirmative%20steps%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20are%20enabled%20and%20empowered%20enough%20to%20be%20participative%20in%20the%20maintream%20decision-making%20process%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703563086000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26092503%2F27905720280_4def8d5561_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Findia-judiciary-courts-pendency-causes-caste-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Research%20and%20Planning%2C%20in%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20report%2C%20has%20looked%20at%20some%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20reasons%20contributing%20to%20pendencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Findia-judiciary-courts-pendency-causes-caste-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir-Alia%2C%20Raha%20And%20Others%20In%20Pics%20From%20The%20Kapoors'%20Christmas%20Lunch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20fam-jam%20time%20for%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Falia-bhatt-ranbir-kapoor-with-daughter-raha-navya-agastya-nanda-at-the-kapoor-family-christmas-lunch-4739760%5C%22%3E%20Kapoors%20and%20the%20Nandas%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20annual%20Christmas%20lunch%20hosted%20by%20Kunal%20Kapoor%20at%20his%20Mumbai%20residence.%20The%20fam-jam%20photos%20feature%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20along%20with%20daughter%20Raha.%20The%20picture%20also%20features%20Aadar%20Jain%20with%20his%20new%20girlfriend%20Alekha%20Advani%2C%20Navya%20Naveli%20Nanda%20with%20brother%20Agastya%20Nanda%20and%20dad%20Nikhil%20Nanda.%20Shashi%20Kapoor's%20grandson%20Zahan%20Kapoor%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20posing%20in%20the%20photos.%20We%20also%20spotted%20Karisma%20and%20her%20dad%20Randhir%20Kapoor%20and%20her%20mom%20Babita.%20Karisma's%20kids%20Samaira%20and%20Kiaan%20Raj%20Kapoor%20also%20feature%20in%20the%20frame.%20Armaan%20Jain%20and%20wife%20Anissa%20were%20pictured%20with%20their%20newborn%20baby.%20Rima%20Jain%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20bash.%20%26quot%3BA%20Merry%20Merry%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20Navya%20captioned%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Karisma%20Kapoor%20shared%20some%20inside%20pictures%20and%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHope%20you%20all%20had%20a%20wonderful%20Christmas.%20Missed%20a%20few%20who%20couldn't%20make%20it%20today.%26quot%3B%20Ka