void%20payment%20of%20taxes%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20latest%20arrests%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-arrests-two-senior-employees-chinese-firm-vivo-source-2023-12-23%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVivo%20spokesperson%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20said%20that%20the%20the%20firm%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20deeply%20alarmed%20by%20the%20current%20action%20of%20the%20authorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20arrests%20demonstrate%20continued%20harassment%20and%20as%20such%20induce%20an%20environment%20of%20uncertainty%20amongst%20the%20wider%20industry%20landscape.%20We%20are%20resolute%20in%20using%20all%20legal%20avenues%20to%20address%20and%20challenge%20these%20accusations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20tightened%20the%20monitoring%20of%20activities%20of%20Chinese%20firms%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20border%20stand-off%20in%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703561726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26090416%2FScreenshot-2023-12-26-at-9.04.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fenforcement-directorate-china-vivo-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ED%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20taken%20into%20custody%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20two%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20charges%20of%20money%20laundering%20against%20the%20Indian%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20Chinese%20phone%20manufacturer%2C%20Vivo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fenforcement-directorate-china-vivo-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dense%20Fog%20In%20Delhi%20Delays%20Several%20Flights%2C%20Passengers%20Alerted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20layer%20of%20dense%20fog%20was%20witnessed%20over%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20as%20the%20temperature%20dropped%20to%20almost%207%20degrees%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorning%20visuals%20from%20Delhi's%20India%20Gate%2C%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%2C%20AIIMS%2C%20Safdarjung%2C%20and%20Anand%20Vihar%20areas%20showed%20them%20engulfed%20in%20dense%20fog%20with%20low%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20sought%20refuge%20in%20night%20shelters%20across%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20as%20the%20cold%20wave%20intensified%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20today%20morning%20released%20satellite%20images%20showing%20a%20layer%20of%20fog%20spreading%20over%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20UP's%20Moradabad%2C%20Kanpur%20showed%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20fog%20bringing%20down%20visibility%20to%20almost%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20see%20the%20road%20due%20to%20the%20fog.%20There%20are%20no%20rides%20till%20now%20unlike%20usual.%20It%20is%20risky%20to%20ride%20at%20this%20time%20because%20of%20low%20visibility%20and%20it%20is%20colder%20than%20usual%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rickshaw%20driver%20from%20Moradabad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20night%20security%20guard%20in%20the%20area%20said%20that%20it%20is%20more%20difficult%20to%20work%20at%20night%20because%20of%20the%20cold%20and%20fog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20cold%20and%20now%20because%20of%20fog%2C%20I%20cannot%20see%20anything.%20I%20work%20at%20night%20and%20with%20this%20cold%2C%20it%20is%20really%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20watchman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20were%20seen%20huddled%20around%20bonfires%20along%20the%20roads%20and%20lanes%20to%20beat%20the%20bone-chilling%20cold%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20airport%20experienced%20delays%20in%20both%20arrivals%20and%20departures%20for%20about%2030%20flights%20including%20international%20due%20to%20dense%20fog%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20Flight%20Information%20Display%20System%20data%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20suggested%20that%20the%20fog%20conditions%20are%20likely%20to%20affect%20more%20number%20of%20flights%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20passenger%20advisory%20issued%20by%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20today%20morning%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20landing%20and%20takeoffs%20continue%20at%20Delhi%20Airport%2C%20flights%20that%20are%20not%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20may%20get%20affected.%20Passengers%20are%20requested%20to%20contact%20the%20airline%20concerned%20for%20updated%20flight%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT-III%20Instrument%20Landing%20System%20(ILS)%20is%20technically%20the%20anti-fog%20landing%20system%20initiated%20by%20the%20airport%20authorities%20in%20Delhi%20to%20facilitate%20landing%20when%20the%20runway%20visibility%20is%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20also%20warned%20of%20possible%20health%20impacts%20on%20people%20due%20to%20the%20dense%20fog%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDense%20fog%20contains%20particulate%20matter%20and%20other%20pollutants%20and%20in%20case%20exposed%20it%20gets%20lodged%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20clogging%20them%20and%20decreasing%20their%20functional%20capacity%20which%20increases%20episodes%20of%20wheezing%2C%20coughing%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%26quot%3B%20IMD%20said%20in%20a%20release%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20release%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20fog%20conditions%20may%20tend%20to%20irritate%20the%20membranes%20of%20the%20eye%20causing%20various%20infections%20leading%20to%20redness%20or%20swelling%20of%20the%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3