l%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20don't%20consider%20themselves%20an%20order%20of%20Catholic%20nuns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Sisters%20bring%20light%20and%20satire%20and%20humor%2C%20not%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20any%20religion%20or%20religious%20faith%2C%20quite%20the%20opposite.%20We%20respect%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Corndog%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20make%20light%20of%20is%20the%20hate-filled%20rhetoric%20that%20spouts%20from%20some%20of%20these%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20gets%20misinterpreted%20often%20by%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20protesting%20the%20US%20Republican%20Convention%20in%20Dallas%2C%20TX%2C%20in%201984.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f9f6ba79e5746976a5e42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221956%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20protesting%20the%20US%20Republican%20Convention%20in%20Dallas%2C%20TX%2C%20in%201984.%3Cp%3ECRO%20%2F%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20part%20of%20their%20mission%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bpromulgate%20universal%20joy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bexpiate%20stigmatic%20guilt%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20guilt%20rooted%20in%20the%20human%20condition%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20part%20of%20the%20mission%20is%20more%20difficult%20since%20some%20people%20carry%20%26quot%3Bpainful%20wounds%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20rhetoric%20they've%20heard%20or%20experienced%20in%20faith%20communities%2C%20Corndog%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20taught%20that%20God%20loves%20you%2C%20that%20you're%20surrounded%20by%20guardian%20angels%20that%20protect%20you%2C%20that%20watch%20over%20you%20in%20the%20night%2C%20very%20beautiful%20comforting%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20but%20then%20they%20sneak%20in%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%2C%20'as%20long%20as%20you're%20heterosexual%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20sisters%20do%20is%20we%20make%20it%20okay%20to%20separate%20that%20hate-filled%20rhetoric%20from%20the%20core%20faith%20and%20belief%20that%20that%20person%20was%20connected%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20while%20some%20actions%20of%20the%20Sisters%20are%20well-publicized%2C%20like%20their%20%26quot%3BHunky%20Jesus%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BFoxy%20Mary%26quot%3B%20costume%20competitions%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eother%20activities%2C%20like%20the%20Sisters'%20work%20with%20the%20unhoused%20and%20those%20with%20substance%20abuse%20disorders%2C%20or%20their%20efforts%20to%20connect%20with%20lonely%20or%20suffering%20people%20in%20their%20communities%2C%20are%20often%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20after%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20Pulse%20nightclub.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f9fe450edbc52a8651d91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20after%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20Pulse%20nightclub.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Vogel%20%2F%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20charitable%20work%2C%20the%20Sisters%20receive%20hate%20mail%20daily%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Corndog%20said%2C%20which%20often%20includes%20violent%20and%20homophobic%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20way%20to%20confront%20this%20kind%20of%20hate%20and%20divide%20is%20in%20a%20most%20loving%2C%20divine%20way.%20To%20not%20fear%20them%2C%20to%20not%20hate%20them%2C%20but%20to%20truly%20put%20into%20the%20universe%2C%20whether%20you%20call%20it%20prayer%20or%20otherwise%2C%20a%20hope%20for%20them%20to%20find%20peace%20in%20their%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Corndog%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20find%20a%20pathway%2C%20to%20correct%20the%20error%20of%20their%20ways%2C%20and%20for%20them%20to%20somehow%20find%20enlightenment%20from%20all%20of%20the%20horrific%20hatred%20that%20they%20carry%20in%20their%20heart.%20That%20must%20be%20exhausting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20kind%20of%20hate%20doesn't%20come%20from%20a%20specific%20hate%20or%20religion%2C%20Corndog%20added.%20Instead%2C%20she%20feels%20people%20in%20power%20have%20incorrectly%20interpreted%20religious%20dogma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20never%20hear%20a%20sister%20say%2C%20'you're%20wrong%20to%20believe%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Corndog%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20never%2C%20ever%20want%20anyone%20to%20feel%20judged%20or%20belittled%20for%20having%20faith%20or%20believing%20in%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorndog%20also%20said%20she%20feels%20many%20religious%20people%2C%20if%20they%20learned%20more%20about%20the%20Sisters%2C%20would%20support%20the%20group%20and%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20that%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%20in%20the%20Catholic%20Bible%2C%20often%20used%20sarcasm%20and%20satire%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20injustice%20and%20strengthen%20their%20relationships%20with%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLove%20one%20another%20was%20at%20the%20core%20of%20his%20teaching%2C%20as%20well%20as%20don't%20judge%20yourself%20and%20don't%20judge%20others.%20Those%20are%20really%20the%20only%20two%20divine%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20the%20people%20who%20are%20spreading%20this%20hatred%20and%20this%20fear%20are%20aware%20of%20how%20far%20off%20track%20they%20have%20gotten%20from%20their%20core%20belief.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20Corndog%20said%2C%20she%20does%20not%20wish%20any%20ill%20on%20people%20who%20disagree%20with%20the%20Sisters%20or%20send%20them%20hate%20mail%20and%20sees%20many%20of%20their%20beliefs%20as%20motivated%20by%20fear%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%2C%20a%20fear%20of%20going%20against%20teachings%20they%20have%20been%20learning%20since%20they%20were%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20at%20Out100%20in%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657fa02f50edbc52a8651d9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sisters%20of%20Perpetual%20Indulgence%20at%20Out100%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Shotwell%20%2F%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERegarding%20responding%20to%20such%20hateful%20rhetoric%2C%20Corndog%20first%20advises%20people%20to%20avoid%20engagement%20and%20keep%20themselves%20safe.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20said%2C%20people%20can%20get%20involved%20in%20organizations%20that%20%26quot%3Bcombat%26quot%3B%20hate%20in%20an%20organized%2C%20educated%20manner.%20She%20mentioned%20that%2C%20for%20example%2C%20people%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20area%20could%20join%20movements%20like%20the%20Harvey%20Milk%20LGBTQ%20Democratic%20Club%20or%20a%20chapter%20of%20the%20Young%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20out%20of%20your%20faith%20to%20combat%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Corndog%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20Catholic%20parishes%20and%20priests%20and%20organizations%20who%20have%20publicly%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Sisters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20summed%20up%20her%20advice%20by%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BStay%20alert%2C%20stay%20involved%2C%20and%20know%20your%20limitations%20of%20what%20you%20can%20and%20can't%20handle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodgers%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsister-shalita-corndog-perpetual-indulgence-dodgers-lgbtq-san-francisco-aids-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22pub