istmas%20Wish%20About%20Israel-Hamas%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnited%20States%20Congresswoman%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20was%20recently%20slammed%20on%20the%20internet%20after%20she%20shared%20an%20Instagram%20story%20about%20Christmas%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F12%2F25%2Fnews%2Faoc-slammed-over-christmas-message-about-israel-hamas-war-jew-hate%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20stated%20that%20Jesus%20Christ%20was%20born%20in%20modern-day%20Palestine%2C%20which%20at%20present%20is%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20%26quot%3BIsrael%2C%20a%20violent%20force%26quot%3B.%20Several%20people%20have%20criticised%20her%20on%20what%20they%20feel%20is%20anti-semitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Chritsmas%20eve%2C%20Ms%20Cortez%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20child%20among%20debris%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20said%20that%20she%20is%20praying%20for%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20innocent%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20occupied%20territories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20in%20the%20story%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20story%20of%20Christmas%2C%20Christ%20was%20born%20in%20modern-day%20Palestine%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20government%20engaged%20in%20a%20massacre%20of%20innocents.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20a%20targeted%20population%20being%20indiscriminately%20killed%20to%20protect%20an%20unjust%20leader's%20power.%20Mary%20and%20Joseph%2C%20displaced%20by%20violence%20and%20forced%20to%20flee%2C%20became%20refugees%20in%20Egypt%20with%20a%20newborn%20waiting%20to%20one%20day%20return%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fc9tfq5c_aoc_625x300_26_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20years%20later%2C%20right-wing%20forces%20are%20violently%20occupying%20Bethlehem%20as%20similar%20stories%20unfold%20for%20today's%20Palestinians%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20Bethlehem%20has%20canceled%20this%20year's%20Christmas%20Eve%20celebrations%20out%20of%20both%20(fear%20for%20their)%20safety%20and%20respect.%20And%20yet%2C%20also%20today%2C%20holy%20children%20are%20still%20being%20born%20in%20a%20place%20of%20unspeakable%20violence%20-%20for%20every%20child%20born%2C%20of%20any%20identity%20and%20from%20any%20place%2C%20is%20sacred.%20Especially%20the%20children%20of%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Cortez%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20festival%20is%20about%20standing%20with%20the%20marginalised%20and%20helpless.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20story%20of%20Christmas%20and%20Christ%20himself%20is%20about%20standing%20with%20the%20poor%20and%20powerless%2C%20the%20marginalized%20and%20maligned%2C%20the%20refugees%20and%20immigrants%2C%20the%20outcast%20and%20misunderstood%20without%20exception%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democrat%20politician%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20high%20Christian%20holiday%20is%20about%20honoring%20the%20precious%20sanctity%20of%20a%20family%20that%2C%20if%20the%20story%20were%20to%20unfold%20today%2C%20would%20be%20Jewish%20Palestinians%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20she%20hopes%20for%20peace%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenshot%20of%20her%20story%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20amassed%20a%20variety%20of%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20the%20absolute%20WORST%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20people%20would%20just%20enjoy%20Christmas%20and%20stop%20getting%20so%20social%20justice%20political%20about%20it.%20I%20am%20so%20glad%20that%20when%20I%20was%20Christian%20I%20had%20a%20blast%20on%20Christmas%20and%20didn't%20waste%20my%20time%20engaging%20in%20this%20nonsense.%20It's%20so%20silly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20hasn't%20she%20resigned%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20pointed%20out%20that%20Ms%20Cortez%20failed%20to%20mention%20the%20Israelis%20who%20are%20still%20being%20held%20hostage%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20by%20Hamas%20as%20well%20as%20women%20who%20were%20sexually%20assaulted%20during%20the%20vicious%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAOC%20is%20antisemitic%20but%20people%20refused%20to%20believe%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703559000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fr32b287_alexandria-ocasiocortez-reuters_625x300_04_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-politician-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-slammed-over-christmas-wish-about-israel-hamas-war-4743225%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Cortez%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20story%20of%20Christmas%2C%20Christ%20was%20born%20in%20modern-day%20Palestine%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20government%20engaged%20in%20a%20massacre%20of%20innocents.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-politician-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-slammed-over-christmas-wish-about-israel-hamas-war-4743225%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-politician-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-slammed-over-christmas-wish-about-israel-hamas-war-4743225%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-politician-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-slammed-over-christmas-wish-about-israel-hamas-war-4743225%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20won%20Arizona%20and%20Georgia%20in%202020%20by%20a%20nose.%20Here's%20why%20that'll%20be%20hard%20to%20do%20next%20year.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22428