Farticleshow%2F106277468.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PARTH%20SHASTRI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Fsuspicious-spouses-keep-helpline-ringing%2Farticleshow%2F106277468.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trafficked%20at%2016%2C%20sold%20%26amp%3B%20raped%20for%205yrs%2C%20woman%20escapes%20'hell'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703556515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106277464%2Cimgsize-15924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Ftrafficked-at-16-sold-raped-for-five-years-woman-escapes-daily-hell%2Farticleshow%2F106277438.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20trafficked%20woman%2C%20sold%20by%20her%20cousin%2C%20managed%20to%20escape%20after%20being%20held%20captive%20and%20raped%20for%20five%20years.%20She%20is%20now%20back%20home%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Her%20cousin%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20but%20the%20father%20and%20son%20who%20repeatedly%20raped%20her%20are%20still%20at%20large.%20The%20survivor%20was%20trafficked%20as%20a%20minor%20and%20is%20now%20a%2021-year-old%20mother.%20She%20was%20sold%20to%20a%20man%20in%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana%2C%20for%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20The%20survivor%20tricked%20her%20captor%20and%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20her%20father%20and%20child.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RASHMI%20DROLIA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Ftrafficked-at-16-sold-raped-for-five-years-woman-escapes-daily-hell%2Farticleshow%2F106277438.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Haven't%20India%20Won%20A%20Test%20Series%20In%20South%20Africa%3F%20Factors%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20men's%20cricket%20team%20has%20demonstrated%20their%20dominance%20in%20various%20conditions%20across%20the%20globe.%20However%2C%20there%20remains%20an%20elusive%20quest%20haunting%20their%20illustrious%20Test%20cricket%20history%20-%20a%20series%20victory%20in%20South%20Africa.%20Despite%20India's%20remarkable%20achievements%20in%20Test%20cricket%20in%20recent%20years%20which%20include%20Test%20series%20victories%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20teams%20have%20faced%20challenges%20in%20conquering%20the%20South%20African%20frontier.%20In%20fact%2C%20India%20have%20won%20only%20four%20Test%20matches%20in%20South%20Africa%20in%20three%20decades.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20reasons%20behind%20this%20unattained%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20challenge%20in%20South%20Africa%20is%20the%20pace-friendly%20pitches%20that%20offer%20bounce%20and%20movement%2C%20conditions%20often%20unfamiliar%20to%20Indian%20players%20of%20previous%20eras.%20Different%20generations%20of%20South%20African%20speedsters%20which%20have%20included%20the%20likes%20of%20Allan%20Doland%2C%20Shaun%20Pollock%2C%20Makhaya%20Ntini%2C%20Dale%20Steyn%20and%20now%20Kagiso%20Rabada%20have%20made%20life%20difficult%20for%20Indian%20batters%20with%20consistent%20pace%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20India%20has%20embarked%20on%20eight%20previous%20tours%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20with%20the%20inaugural%20visit%20taking%20place%20during%20the%201992%2F93%20season.%20Under%20the%20captaincy%20of%20Mohammad%20Azharuddin%2C%20the%20team%20participated%20in%20a%20four-match%20Test%20series%2C%20which%20India%20lost%201-0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlien%20conditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPre-tour%20preparation%20for%20India's%20first%20tour%20to%20South%20Africa%20included%20no%20conditioning%20camp%20or%20practice%20matches.%20The%20players%20assembled%20in%20Bombay%20(now%20Mumbai)%20a%20few%20days%20before%20departure%20solely%20to%20obtain%20tour%20clothing%20and%20participate%20in%20the%20traditional%20team%20photo%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20today%20where%20the%20Indian%20team%20travels%20with%20a%20large%20support%20squad%20that%20includes%20net%20bowlers%20and%20reserves%20as%20well%2C%20India's%20support%20staff%20for%20the%20first%20tour%20included%20the%20coach%2C%20physio%20and%20a%20team%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20enduring%20years%20of%20political%20isolation%20and%20cricket%20seclusion%2C%20South%20Africa%20emerged%20as%20the%20superior%20team%2C%20propelled%20by%20the%20formidable%20duo%20of%20Allan%20Donald%20and%20Brett%20Schultz%20spearheading%20the%20South%20African%20bowling%20attack.%20Additionally%2C%20Keppler%20Wessels%2C%20Andrew%20Hudson%2C%20Peter%20Kirsten%2C%20and%20Jonty%20Rhodes%20made%20for%20an%20imposing%20batting%20lineup%20on%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20squad%20for%20the%20Tour%20included%20youngsters%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Anil%20Kumble%20and%20Javagal%20Srinath%20with%20Kapil%20Dev%20in%20the%20twilight%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20maiden%20tour%2C%20India%20revisited%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%201996%2F97%20and%202001%2F02%20seasons.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Team%20India%20couldn't%20secure%20a%20Test%20match%20victory%20on%20either%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team's%20struggles%20to%20consistently%20produce%20a%20potent%20pace%20attack%20capable%20of%20exploiting%20the%20bounce%20and%20movement%20offered%20by%20the%20pitches%20continued%20to%20haunt%20them.%20The%20inability%20to%20consistently%20take%20wickets%20hampered%20India's%20chances%20of%20securing%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistoric%20win%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20technology%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20better%20exposure%20before%20the%20tours%2C%20Indian%20bowlers%20started%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20conditions%20better%20as%20the%20years%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20African%20team%2C%20led%20by%20Graeme%20Smith%2C%20were%20firm%20favourites%20to%20win%20the%20three-match%20Test%20series%20in%202006.%20However%2C%20India%20achieved%20a%20historic%20feat%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20Test%20at%20the%20New%20Wanderers%20Stadium%20in%20Johannesburg.%20Marked%20by%20stellar%20performances%20from%20pacers%20S%20Sreesanth%20and%20Zaheer%20Khan%2C%20India%20clinched%20their%20first-ever%20Test%20win%20on%20South%20African%20soil%20and%20took%20a%201-0%20lead%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20captaincy%20of%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20India%20posted%20249%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20after%20choosing%20to%20bat%20first.%20The%20team%20then%20bowled%20out%20South%20Africa%20for%20a%20mere%2084%20with%20Sreesanth%20leading%20the%20charge%20with%205%2F40.%20India%20managed%20236%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20to%20put%20on%20a%20target%20of%20401%20for%20South%20Africa%2C%20who%20were%20dismissed%20for%20278%20in%20response.%20India%20won%20the%20first%20Test%20by%20123%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20good%20outing%20practice%20in%20the%20tour%20match%20in%20Potchefstroom%20a%20week%20before%20the%20Test%20and%20South%20Africa%20had%20lost%20two%20of%20their%20last%20three%20Tests%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20against%20England%20and%20Australia%20which%20helped%20the%20Indian%20side%20study%20those%20matches%20and%20prepare%20better%20for%20the%20Test%20series.%20Despite%20taking%20a%201-0%20lead%2C%20India%20eventually%20lost%20the%20series%201-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMS%20Dhoni%20era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMS%20Dhoni%20was%20the%20captain%20for%20the%202010%2F11%20tour%20and%20Team%20India%20secured%20their%20second%20victory%20in%20the%20format%20in%20South%20Africa.%20Though%20India%20lost%20the%20first%20match%20at%20Centurion%20by%20an%20innings%20and%2025%20runs%2C%20Harbhajan%20Singh's%204%2F10%20helped%20India%20restrict%20South%20Africa%20to%20131%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20second%20match%20in%20Durban%20after%20India%20posted%20205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVVS%20Laxman's%20gritty%2096%20helped%20India%20post%20228%20runs%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20before%20S%20Sreesanth%20and%20Zaheer%20Khan%20claimed%20three%20wickets%20each%20to%20bowl%20out%20South%20Africa%20for%20215%20and%20secure%20India's%2087-run%20victory.%20The%20third%20Test%20at%20Cape%20Town%20concluded%20in%20a%20draw%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%201-1%20finish%20for%20the%20three-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%20in%202013%2C%20India%20flew%20to%20South%20Africa%20for%20a%20two-match%20Test%20series.%20India%20lost%20the%20Test%20series%201-0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%20Kohli's%20reign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202017%2F18%20season%2C%20India%2C%20led%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20embarked%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20engaging%20in%20a%20three-Test%20series%20that%20commenced%20with%20a%20disheartening%2072-run%20loss%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20The%20series%20deficit%20deepened%20to%200-2%20following%20a%20135-run%20defeat%20in%20the%20second%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setbacks%2C%20India%20staged%20a%20remarkable%20turnaround%2C%20clinching%20a%2063-run%20victory%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20at%20Johannesburg%2C%20ending%20the%20series%20with%20a%202-1%20result.%20Pacers%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%20played%20pivotal%20roles%2C%20each%20securing%20five-wicket%20hauls%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20innings%2C%20respectively%2C%20averting%20a%20potential%20whitewash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20triumphs%20in%20South%20Africa%20were%20further%20boosted%20during%20the%202021%2F22%20tour.%20The%20series%20commenced%20with%20India%20achieving%20their%20inaugural%20Test%20victory%20at%20SuperSport%20Park%20in%20Centurion%2C%20finally%20succeeding%20after%20two%20prior%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20KL%20Rahul's%20resilient%20knock%20of%20123%20powered%20India%20to%20a%20total%20of%20327%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%20The