aii-HELP-Program-Overview-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20two-year%20commitment%20is%20required%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20program%2C%20and%20continuation%20is%20then%20evaluated%20on%20a%20year-by-year%20basis.%20The%20worker%20must%20be%20licensed%20in%20Hawaii%20to%20qualify%2C%20and%20they%20must%20take%20a%20minimum%2030%25%20of%20patience%20on%20public%20insurance.%20Those%20who%20wish%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20next%20cohort%20can%20do%20so%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahec.hawaii.edu%2Fhawai%25CA%25BBi-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20program%20is%20funded%20with%20%2430%20million%20from%20the%20Hawaii%20state%20legislature%20and%20an%20additional%20%245%20million%20from%20the%20CEO%20of%20Salesforce%2C%20Mark%20Benioff%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Lynne%20Benioff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHawaii's%20program%20is%20just%20one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20efforts%20on%20the%20state%20level%20to%20get%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20borrowers.%20In%20Maine%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20state's%20lawmakers%20in%202022%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaine-willl-pay-student-loan-debt-if-you-buy-house-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20proposing%20up%20to%20%2440%2C000%20in%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20efforts%20come%20as%20the%20fate%20of%20broader%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20remains%20uncertain%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estruck%20down%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20the%20same%20day%20that%20it%20would%20be%20pursuing%20a%20narrower%20scale%20of%20relief%20using%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-student-loan-borrowers-will-get-debt-cancellation-biden-hardship-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econcluded%20negotiations%20with%20stakeholders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20what%20the%20text%20of%20the%20relief%20should%20look%20like%2C%20and%20the%20public%20can%20expect%20an%20opportunity%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20proposals%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20millions%20of%20federal%20borrowers%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereturn%20to%20repayment%20after%20an%20over-three-year%20pause%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20With%20the%20burden%20of%20an%20additional%20monthly%20bill%2C%20many%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20when%2C%20or%20if%2C%20they%20will%20see%20a%20reduction%20in%20their%20balances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20targeted%20programs%2C%20like%20the%20one%20Hawaii%20is%20implementing%20for%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20might%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20one%20of%20the%20key%20lessons%20we've%20learned%20over%20the%20years%20is%20we%20simply%20don't%20have%20enough%20healthcare%20providers%20in%20the%20places%20we%20need%20the%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspectrumlocaln