0had%20had%20a%20spiritual%20awakening%20of%20sorts%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20and%20felt%20compelled%20to%20share%20the%20joy%20of%20the%20Christmas%20story%20with%20all%208000%20inmates%20of%20Tihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20excited%20was%20he%20about%20his%20project%20that%20he%20had%20already%20assembled%20a%20theatre%20troupe%20from%20amongst%20the%20other%20foreign%20inmates%20and%20had%20begun%20rehearsals.%C2%A0%20He%20showed%20us%20the%20script%20he%20had%20written.%20It%20was%20original.%20His%20notes%20for%20the%20Third%20Act%20read%20thus%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAct%203%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%201%3A%20Joseph%20and%20Mary%20on%20way%20to%20Bethlehem.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%202%3A%20Joseph%20gets%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20police%20on%20false%20charges%20of%20possessing%20drugs%20and%20is%20thrown%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%203%3A%20There%2C%20he%20meets%20Noah%20who%20has%20been%20incarcerated%20for%20attempting%20to%20build%20a%20boat%20without%20a%20proper%20license.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%2C%20man.%20Needs%20a%20little%20masala%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckled%20as%20he%20introduced%20us%20to%20the%20actors%20in%20his%20ensemble.%20Inmates%20of%20various%20nationalities%2C%20some%20undertrials%20and%20others%2C%20convicts%2C%20were%20chosen%20to%20play%20the%20roles%20of%20the%20kings%2C%20the%20shepherds%20and%20the%20angels.%20A%20short%2C%20stocky%20Nigerian%20was%20selected%20to%20play%20Joseph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20asked%20Nigel%20the%20question%20that%20had%20been%20bothering%20me%20from%20the%20time%20we%20first%20heard%20about%20this%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20are%20you%20doing%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20Christmas%20play%20without%20a%20Mary%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nigel%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20see%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20Mary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20responded%20cheerily%20and%20introduced%20us%20to%20a%20tall%2C%20bald%2C%20unsmiling%20Dutchman.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20put%20a%20shawl%20and%20a%20lipstick%20on%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20worst%20fear%20had%20just%20been%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERehearsals%20were%20held%20for%20the%20play%20every%20morning%20and%20every%20evening%20for%202%20weeks.%20Also%20part%20of%20the%20play%20were%20Christmas%20carols%20to%20be%20performed%20by%20a%20choir%20of%2012%20Nigerian%20inmates.%20They%20looked%20good%20on%20stage%20and%20moved%20well%20together%20as%20they%20sang.%20The%20only%20problem%20was%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20tone%20deaf%20and%20Chuck%20and%20Thomas%2C%20the%20biggest%20and%20worst%20tempered%20of%20the%20lot%2C%20did%20not%20get%20along.%20But%20these%20were%20minor%20issues%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things.%20We%20had%20bigger%20things%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20toughest%20part%20of%20the%20production%2C%20however%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20choir!%20They%20just%20could%20not%20carry%20a%20tune.%20With%20only%20ten%20days%20to%20go%20for%20the%20first%20show%20and%20tensions%20running%20high%2C%20I%20called%20a%20friend%20who%20owned%20a%20studio%20and%20asked%20him%20for%20advice.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20create%20music%20tracks%20for%20you%20that%20these%20chaps%20can%20sing%20on.%20Make%20sure%20the%20music%20is%20louder%20than%20the%20vocals.%20It%20just%20might%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20did!%20The%20singers%20were%20thrilled%20to%20discover%20that%20they%20actually%20could%20sing%20karaoke%20style%20to%20backing%20music%20tracks.%20So%20inspired%20were%20they%20with%20their%20new%20ability%20to%20sound%20melodic%20that%20they%20practiced%20for%20two%20days%20straight%20without%20fighting%20and%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20the%20second%20day%20managed%20to%20sing%20%3Cem%3EJingle%20Bells%2C%20O%20Come%20All%20Ye%20faithful%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESilent%20Night%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20same%20key.%20The%20relief%20was%20huge.%20They%20fist%20bumped%20and%20high-fived%2C%20and%20that%20night%20I%20slept%20in%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecember%2018%2C%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20of%20the%20first%20Christmas%20show%20arrived.%20The%20Tihar%20Theatre%20Troupe%20was%20to%20debut%20in%20Jail%20No.%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigel%2C%20every%20inch%20the%20nervous%20director%2C%20gave%20last%20minute%20instructions%20to%20the%20actors%20who%20took%20up%20positions%20behind%20the%20stage.%20The%202000-strong%20population%20of%20the%20jail%20filed%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echakkar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20common%20area%20used%20for%20cultural%20events%20and%20started%20sitting%20in%20rows%20under%20the%20watchful%20eyes%20of%20the%20white%20%3Cem%3Ekurta%20pajama%3C%2Fem%3E%20clad%20%3Cem%3Enumberdaars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20convicts%20charged%20with%20maintaining%20order%20amongst%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20inmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20327px)%2085vw%2C%20327px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22327%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20625w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-188x300.jpg%20188w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690663%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERohit%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ETales%20from%20the%20Jail%20%E2%80%93%20Christmas%20in%20Tihar%20and%20Other%20Stories%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ENotion%20Press%2C%202016%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20something%20