20in%20peals%20of%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Baby%20Jesus%20(a%20cloth%20doll)%20was%20about%20to%20come%20into%20the%20world%2C%20Joseph%20knelt%20beside%20Mary%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCome%20on%2C%20Mary%2C%20push!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%20I%20heard%20someone%20in%20the%20audience%20mimicking%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20cry.%20Others%20imitated%20and%20soon%20about%20a%20thousand%20people%20joined%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20it%20happened!%20The%20moment%20of%20Jesus%E2%80%99%20birth!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20stood%20up%2C%20holding%20not%20a%20cloth%20doll%20but%20a%20real%20live%20baby%20in%20his%20arms!%20The%20crowd%20went%20wild.%20I%20lost%20my%20power%20of%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20later%20discovered%2C%20some%20of%20our%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20the%20shepherds%20to%20be%20precise%20%E2%80%93%20had%20discovered%20a%20baby%20behind%20the%20stage.%20It%20was%20the%20child%20of%20a%20woman%20labourer%20who%20along%20with%20others%20had%20been%20brought%20into%20the%20jail%20to%20do%20construction%20work.%20The%20actors%20had%20%E2%80%98borrowed%E2%80%99%20the%20baby%20and%20managed%20to%20pass%20it%20on%20to%20Mary%20and%20Joseph%20on%20stage.%20It%20was%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20the%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20kings%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20in%20Indian%20king%20costumes%20replete%20with%20Indian%20crowns%20and%20Indian%20beads%20%E2%80%93%20walked%20in%20and%20offered%20%E2%80%98gifts%20of%20gold%2C%20frankincense%20and%20myrrh%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20And%20as%20they%20knelt%20before%20Indian%20baby%20Jesus%2C%20the%20choir%20walked%20up%20on%20stage%2C%20surrounded%20the%20nativity%20scene%20and%20sang%20%E2%80%98Silent%20Night%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20silence%20that%20followed.%20The%20Nigerian%20choir%20sang%20pitch-perfect.%20They%20were%20magical!%20Was%20this%20the%20same%20choir%20that%20had%20come%20to%20blows%20just%20days%20before%3F%20The%20actors%20joined%20in%20as%20did%20those%20few%20in%20the%20audience%20who%20knew%20the%20carol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSilent%20Night%2C%20Holy%20Night%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20is%20calm%2C%20all%20is%20bright%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20they%20finished%20singing%2C%20a%20hush%20had%20fallen%20on%20the%20crowd.%20Some%20sort%20of%20heavenly%20peace%20had%20indeed%20descended%20on%20Jail%20No.%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20ended%20and%20Nigel%20gave%20one%20last%20speech.%20It%20was%20halting%20and%20went%20something%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFriends%2C%20I%20know%20Diwali%20was%20a%20difficult%20day%20for%20you.%20You%20wanted%20to%20spend%20it%20with%20your%20family%20but%20you%20spent%20it%20here%20in%20jail.%20This%20is%20my%20first%20Christmas%20away%20from%20home%20too.%20Mary%20and%20Joseph%20were%20far%20away%20from%20home%20too.%20In%20the%20company%20of%20strangers.%20And%20yet%2C%20they%20were%20not%20alone.%20Neither%20are%20we.%20Christmas%20reminds%20me%20that%20we%20are%20never%20alone%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20And%20when%20you%20think%20there%20is%20no%20hope%20left%2C%20something%20wonderful%20will%20happen.%20I%20know%20it%20will.%20And%20you%20will%20be%20given%20the%20strength%20to%20carry%20on.%20Tomorrow%20will%20be%20better%20than%20yesterday.%20Merry%20Christmas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20the%20crowd%20dispersed%20and%20started%20heading%20back%20to%20their%20barracks%20in%20high%20spirits.%20The%20actors%20laughed%2C%20hugged%20and%20congratulated%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20have%20since%20passed.%20I%20lost%20touch%20with%20Nigel%20and%20his%20team%20after%20he%20got%20acquitted.%20But%20every%20December%20I%20remember%20the%20Tihar%20Theatre%20Troupe%20and%20give%20thanks%20for%20the%20memory%20of%20Christmas%2