0of%20them%20have%20already%20been%20killed.%20So%2C%20how%20is%20this%20%E2%80%98Khushal%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20where%20neither%20Armymen%20nor%20common%20people%20are%20safe%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20national%20parties%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20has%20also%20strongly%20condemned%20what%20they%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20brutal%20killing%20of%20three%20civilians%20in%20the%20Poonch%20district%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20while%20they%20were%20in%20custody%20of%20the%20army.%E2%80%9D%20Stating%20that%20just%20compensation%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0announced%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20the%20party%20added%20that%20there%20must%20be%20a%20speedy%20investigation%20and%20punishment%20meted%20out%20to%20those%20responsible.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20who%20have%20long%20suffered%20from%20such%20acts%20of%20impunity%2C%20expect%20accountability%20to%20be%20fixed%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20justice%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpim.org%2Fpressbriefs%2Fjk-act-end-such-impunity%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703440933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24194348%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-24-at-6.20.20-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoonch-civilians-killed-are-among-the-men-seen-in-video-being-tortured-by-soldiers-sarpanch-confirms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allegation%20of%20custodial%20torture%20and%20killing%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20370%20judgment%2C%20Army%20says%20matter%20is%20%E2%80%98under%20invest