e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20violence%20and%20atrocities%20that%20I%20have%20witnessed%20during%20the%20course%20of%20my%20political%20career%20has%20ensured%20nothing%20really%20shocks%20or%20rattles%20me%20anymore.%20But%20I%20was%20left%20stunned%20by%20a%20gruesome%2C%20abominable%20video%20that%20is%20doing%20the%20rounds%20over%20social%20media.%20The%20video%2C%20little%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20long%2C%20shows%20Army%20%3Cem%3Ejawans%3C%2Fem%3E%20clad%20in%20uniforms%20using%20abusive%20language%20while%20mercilessly%20thrashing%20civilians%20who%20appear%20to%20be%20half%20dead.%20Not%20satisfied%20with%20lashing%20them%20with%20sticks%2C%20they%20then%20go%20onto%20to%20strip%20them%20naked%20and%20pour%20heaps%20of%20red%20chilli%20powder%20on%20their%20gashed%20and%20wounded%20bottoms.%20A%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20video%20was%20verified%2C%20another%20disturbing%20fact%20came%20to%20light.%20One%20of%20those%20innocent%20civilians%20was%20already%20dead%20while%20this%20act%20of%20violence%20was%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deeply%20distressing%20question%20came%20to%20mind.%20Who%20would%20dare%20to%20shoot%20such%20a%20video%20under%20those%20circumstances%3F%20Certainly%20not%20a%20civilian.%20Clearly%20it%20was%20one%20of%20them.%20The%20video%20was%20deliberately%20leaked%20and%20disseminated%20with%20the%20diabolical%20intention%20of%20conveying%20a%20chilling%20message.%20By%20the%20very%20same%20persons%20whose%20unprecedented%20presence%20through%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20justified%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20securing%20our%20lives.%20This%20is%20the%20side%20of%20the%20story%20that%20the%20media%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20you%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shameful%20incident%20took%20place%20after%20five%20Army%20men%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%20by%20militants%20in%20Poonch.%20Its%20certainly%20not%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20years%20that%20the%20Army%20has%20suffered%20huge%20casualties%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Pir%20Panchal%20area%20never%20gravitated%20towards%20militancy.%20The%20last%20two%20decades%20witnessed%20relative%20peace%20in%20the%20area%20where%20people%20have%20cooperated%20in%20every%20manner%20possible%20with%20the%20armed%20forces.%20For%20militancy%20to%20erupt%20here%20is%20a%20worrying%20sign.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20false%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20wiped%20out%20terrorism%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20This%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20has%20now%20engulfed%20even%20a%20region%20like%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20which%20have%20remained%20peaceful%20even%20during%20peak%20insurgency%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Poison%20Has%20Now%20Reached%20India%E2%80%99s%20Schools%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20a%20retired%20SP%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20a%20mosque%20in%20Baramulla%20despite%20a%20heavy%20security%20presence%2C%20The%20falsehood%20created%20and%20propagated%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20about%20Article%20370%20being%20responsible%20for%20unrest%20and%20violence%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20stands%20exposed.%20This%20is%20the%20argument%20that%20was%20invoked%20for%20their%20unconstitutional%20and%20illegal%20action%20of%20scrapping%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20special%20status.%20In%20doing%20so%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20desecrate%20our%20special%20constitution%20but%20also%20subverted%20the%20constitution%20of%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20offered%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20to%20undo%20this%20political%20%3Cem%3Eharakiri%3C%2Fem%3E%20ignored%20its%20own%20earlier%20decisions%20and%20went%20along%20with%20the%20majoritarian%20sentiment.%20To%20put%20facts%20into%20perspective%2C%20in%20cases%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F879068%2F%5C%22%3ESampat%20Prakash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F153910827%2F%5C%22%3EVijay%20Lakshmi%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20top%20court%20upheld%20that%20Article%20370%20though%20a%20temporary%20provision%20can%20be%20scrapped%20only%20with%20the%20recommendation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20constituent%20assembly%20to%20the%20president.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20no%20other%20institution%20including%20parliament%20had%20the%20right%20to%20tamper%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20and%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20the%20supreme%20authority%20and%20cannot%20be%20overruled%20by%20a%20government%20that%20commands%20brute%20majority%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Even%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20bound%20to%20uphold%20its%20provisions.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20to%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20constitution%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20corner.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20minorities%20are%20being%20reduced%20to%20second%20class%20citizens%2C%20as%20residents%20of%20the%20only%20Muslim%20majority%20state%20which%20has%20been%20dismembered%20and%20disempowered%20after%202019%2C%20it%20was%20natural%20for%20us%20to%20place%20some%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary.%20Alas%2C%20even%20this%20glimmer%20of%20faith%20was%20misplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20verdict%20was%20a%20test%20for%20the%20honourable%20institution%20to%20not%20only%20uphold%20its%20earlier%20judgements%20regarding%20J%26amp%3BK%20but%20also%20save%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20from%20being%20undermined%20even%20further.%20For%20those%20of%20us%20who%20believe%20and%20cherish%20the%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20like%20a%20bridge%20that%20connected%20us%20to%20the%20country.%20It%20had%20little%20importance%20for%20those%20who%20nurtured%20the%20sentiment%20of%20separatism.%20By%20doing%20away%20with%20it%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20obliterated%20the%20middle%20ground%20that%20pushed%20for%20democracy%20and%20peace%20with%20dignity.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20strengthened%20the%20narrative%20of%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-without-elected-government-five-years%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20In%205%20Years%20Without%20Elected%20Govt%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Crown%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20Has%20Become%20a%20Khap%20Panchayat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facade%20of%20normalcy%20continues%20to%20exact%20a%20heavy%20price%20from%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20They%20have%20to%20pay%20with%20their%20lives%20and%20liberty%20to%20maintain%20a%20sullen%20silence.%20For%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20the%20uptick%20in%20tourism%20has%20become%20a%20marker%20for%20its%20fake%20narrative%20of%20normalcy%20and%20is%20touted%20to%20strengthen%20its%20claim%20of%20establishing%20peace%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20a%20visiting%20tourist%20enjoys%20his%20short%20stay%20in%20the%20valley.%20Because%20unlike%20its%20inhabitants%2C%20he%20is%20not%20subjected%20to%20suspicion%2C%20religious%20prejudice%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20anti%20terror%20laws%20like%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA).%20Nor%20does%20the%20sword%20of%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20or%20the%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20hang%20over%20their%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmiri%20youngsters%20are%20packed%20off%20to%20jails%20in%20and%20outside%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20trivial%20grounds.%20Businessmen%20and%20even%20small%20time%20entrepreneurs%20are%20raided%20day%20in%20and%20out%20just%20to%20instil%20fear%20within%20the%20community.%20Journalists%20whose%20duty%20is%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20are%20put%20behind%20bars%20for%20their%20reportage.%20Government%20employees%20are%20gagged%20through%20official%20orders%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20articulating%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20own%20admission%2C%20countless%20properties%20of%20common%20people%20too%20have%20been%20sealed%20without%20even%20giving%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20defend%20themselves.%20Even%20religious%20heads%20like%20%3Cem%3Emaulvis%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eimaams%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F936380%2Fin-kashmir-a-quiet-crackdown-on-mosques-and-clerics%5C%22%3Etold%20what%20to%20include%20in%20their%20weekly%20sermons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20masses%20cannot%20protest%20peacefully%20even%20about%20day%20to%20day%20issues%20like%20gruelling%20power%20cuts%20that%20affect%20their%20lives.%20Even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmismatch-between-home-ministrys-report-on-jk-investments-and-its-statement-in-lok-sabha%2Farticle66334247.ece%5C%22%3EUnion%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20getting%20huge%20investment%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20patent%20lie.%20All%20major%20government%20recruitment%20schemes%20since%202019%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20scams%2C%20one%20after%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%20has%20changed%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20is%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20which%20was%20ahead%20of%20model%20states%20in%20terms%20of%20development%20indices%20is%20now%20lagging%20behind.%20There%20is%20growing%20unemployment%20(one%20of%20the%20highest%20rates%20in%20the%20country)%2C%20our%20local%20economy%20has%20been%20battered%20and%20even%20developmental%20contracts%20are%20being%20outsourced%20to%20outsiders%20who%20sublet%20it%20to%20locals%20after%20extorting%20a%20monumental%20commission.%20A%20beautiful%20prosperous%20state%20like%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20being%20torn%20apart%20psychologically%2C%20financially%20and%20socially.%20All%20this%20in%20the%20name%20of%20integrating%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20fact%20is%20that%20this%20state%20and%20the%20pain%20inflicted%20on%20its%20people%20will%20always%20be%20used%20to%20earn%20votes%20throughout%20the%20country.%20Far%20from%20the%20show%20window%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20promised%20to%20transform%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%2C%20it%20is%20now%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20ruin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20article%20made%20reference%20to%20a%20fourth%20civilian%20death%2C%20reports%20of%20which%20were%20unconfirmed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703427624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-facade-of-normalcy-exacts-a-heavy-price-from-the-people-of-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kashmiri%20youngsters%20are%20packed%20off%20to%20jails%20in%20and%20outside%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20trivial%20grounds%20while%20the%20rest%20pay%20with%20their%20lives%20and%20liberty%20to%20maintain%20a%20sullen%20silence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-facade-of-normalcy-exacts-a-heavy-price-from-the-people-of-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tanker%20Hit%20off%20Gujarat%20Coast%20by%20Drone%20Fired%20From%20Iran%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20According%20to%20the%20US%20military%2C%20a%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%20has%20hit%20a%20Japanese-owned%20chemical%20tanker%20located%20around%20370%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Indian%20coast%20off%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67811929%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2024.%20Though%20the%20hit%20caused%20structural%20damage%2C%20no%20casualties%20have%20been%20reported%20and%20a%20fire%20aboard%20the%20tanker%20was%20put%20out.%20The%20Indian%20navy%20has%20sent%20an%20aircraft%20and%20warships%20for%20assistance%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BBC%20reported%20that%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20that%20the%20tanker%20%E2%80%93%20named%20%E2%80%9CChem%20Pluto%E2%80%9D%2C%20donning%20a%20Liberian%20flag%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20Netherlands%20%E2%80%93%20was%20hit%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20one-way%20attack%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%E2%80%9D.%20The%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20per%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20US%20military%20is%20in%20communication%20with%20the%20vessel%20%E2%80%9Cas%20it%20continues%20toward%20a%20destination%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20December%2023%20(06%3A00%20GMT)%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukmto.org%2Findian-ocean%2Frecent-incidents%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnited%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(UKMTO)%2C%20which%20provides%20information%20on%20maritime%20security%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20The%20UKMTO%20reported%20that%20it%20received%20news%20of%20an%20attack%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20200%20NM%20%5Bnautical%20miles%5D%20South%20West%20of%20Veraval%2C%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cauthorities%20are%20investigating%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20drone%20and%20missile%20strikes%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHouthi%20rebels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Iran-backed%20group%20which%20controls%20a%20large%20part%20of%20Yemen%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20shipping%20route.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20attacks%20began%20after%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20with%20the%20Houthis%20declaring%20their%20support%20for%20Hamas.%20Their%20means%20of%20showing%20this%20support%20has%20been%20by%20attacking%20cargo%20and%20commercial%20vessels%20bound%20for%2C%20or%20linked%20to%2C%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20shipping%20companies%20have%20stopped%20going%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20choosing%20to%20reroute%20their%20vessels%20south%20of%20Africa%20despite%20the%20longer%20route%20and%20higher%20fuel%20costs.%20The%20US%2C%20along%20with%20more%20than%2020%20countries%2C%20has%20set%20up%20a%20multinational%20naval%20task%20force%20to%20protect%20ship%20movements%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20US%20has%20openly%20accused%20Iran%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20support%20Hamas%2C%20of%20directly%20targeting%20ships%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Per%20the%20BBC%2C%20Iran%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20drone%20attack%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20vessel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Israel%20had%20alleged%20that%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20Houthi%20rebels%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20hijacking%20of%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%5C%22%3E%20Israeli-linked%20cargo%20ship%20headed%20from%20Turkey%20to%20India%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20hijacked%20vessel%20had%20been%20in%20Korfez%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Pipavav%2C%20India%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20seizure%20reported%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703422437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftanker-hit-off-gujarat-coast-by-drone-fired-from-iran-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20attack%20caused%20damages%20to%20the%20Japanese-owned%20ship%2C%20no%20casualties%20have%20been%20reported%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftanker-hit-off-gujarat-coast-by-drone-fired-from-iran-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Crime%20Is%20Mine%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Everyone%20Wants%20To%20Be%20a%20Murderess%20In%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Ozon%E2%80%99s%20Feathery%20French%20Farce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703420770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FThe-Crime-is-Mine.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235850129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quick%2C%20silly%20and%20lent%20weight%20only%20by%20the%20costume%20department%E2%80%99s%20copious%20wigs%20and%20furs%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Crime%20Is%20Mine%E2%80%9D%20finds%20tireless%20French%20auteur%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Ozon%20in%20the%20playful%20period%20pastiche%20mode%20of%20%E2%80%9CPotiche%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C8%20Women.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20film%20less%20about%20any%20frenetic%20onscreen%20shenanigans%20as%20it%20is%20about%20its%20own%20mood%20board%20of%20sartorial%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guy%20Lodge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20the%20IMA%20Cheering%20If%20Doctors%20Are%20Still%20Punishable%20for%20Medical%20Negligence%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F01124355%2FDYF-camp.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%2022%20December%2C%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20organisation%20representing%20doctors%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20extended%20its%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20via%20a%20daily%20newspaper%20advertisement%20for%20%E2%80%9Cexempting%20medical%20professionals%20from%20criminal%20prosecution%20under%20304(a)%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20now%2026%20of%20BNS%20(death%20by%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gesture%20followed%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20in%20Parliament%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20the%20three%20criminal%20reform%20Bills%20were%20passed%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20provisions%20related%20to%20death%20resulting%20from%20medical%20negligence%20would%20be%20excluded%20from%20Section%2026%20of%20the%20new%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pledged%20an%20amendment%20to%20shield%20doctors%20from%20potential%20legal%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20not%20exempt%20from%20punishment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20passage%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20doctors%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20receive%20outright%20immunity%20in%20cases%20of%20death%20due%20to%20negligence%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20BNS.%20Instead%2C%20the%20legislation%20maintains%20a%20maximum%20two-year%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20this%20is%20a%20slightly%20reduced%20penalty%20compared%20to%20other%20death-related%20offences%2C%20the%20punishments%20for%20which%20have%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20BNS%2C%20the%20punishment%20for%20causing%20accidental%20death%20(like%20road%20traffic%20death)%20was%20increased%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20five%20years.%20An%20additional%20provision%20was%20introduced%20for%20situations%20where%20the%20responsible%20party%20flees%20or%20fails%20to%20report%20the%20incident%2C%20allowing%20for%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20amendment%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20such%20an%20act%20is%20done%20by%20a%20registered%20medical%20practitioner%20while%20performing%20a%20medical%20procedure%2C%20he%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20two%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20a%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20criminal%20cases%20can%20still%20be%20filed%20against%20medical%20professionals%20for%20deaths%20arising%20from%20medical%20negligence%2C%20but%20the%20maximum%20imprisonment%20is%20now%20less%20severe%20compared%20to%20other%20death-related%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20why%20is%20the%20IMA%20happy%20about%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20will%20maintain%20the%20maximum%20imprisonment%20for%20doctors%20at%20the%20same%20level%20as%20specified%20under%20Section%20304(A)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20allowing%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20original%20draft%20of%20the%20Bill%20had%20asked%20for%20seven%20years%20of%20punishment%20for%20death%20due%20to%20negligence.%20We%20made%20a%20submission%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20to%20differentiate%20medical%20death%20by%20a%20doctor%20from%20death%20due%20to%20negligence.%20Later%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20lowered%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20President-elect%20of%20IMA%2C%20Dr%20V%20Asokan%2C%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Home%20Minister%20accepted%20the%20demand%20and%20differentiated%20medical%20negligence.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20the%20minister%20went%20beyond%20this%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20explicitly%20stating%20that%20deaths%20during%20treatment%20were%20no%20longer%20to%20be%20considered%20as%20murder.%20The%20minister%20expressed%20the%20intention%20to%20exempt%20doctors%20from%20such%20scenarios%20through%20an%20upcoming%20amendment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Asokan%20added%20that%20the%20parliamentary%20declaration%20by%20the%20Home%20Minister%20signifies%20a%20departure%20from%20previous%20norms%2C%20affirming%20that%20any%20death%20during%20treatment%20is%20not%20to%20be%20deemed%20as%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20essence%2C%20the%20government%20has%20declared%2C%20in%20principle%2C%20its%20acceptance%20of%20the%20IMA%E2%80%99s%20stance%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminality%20involved%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient.%20The%20IMA%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminal%20intention%20between%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient%2C%20emphasising%20that%20criminality%20requires%20intent%20to%20harm%2C%20and%20crime%20is%20defined%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20criminal%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20negligence%20as%20per%20the%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20negligence%20is%20subject%20to%20provisions%20influenced%20by%20case%20laws%2C%20particularly%20relevant%20Supreme%20Court%20judgements%20like%20Jacob%20Mathew%20vs%20State%20of%20Punjab%2C%20dealing%20with%20medical%20negligence%20and%20the%20criminal%20liability%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20and%20resulted%20in%20the%20formulation%20of%20important%20guidelines%20regarding%20the%20prosecution%20of%20doctors%20for%20offences%20related%20to%20medical%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20a%20doctor%2C%20Jacob%20Mathew%2C%20accused%20of%20causing%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20death%20due%20to%20medical%20negligence.%20Dr%20Mathew%20challenged%20criminal%20proceedings%2C%20arguing%20that%20a%20medical%20professional%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20held%20criminally%20liable%20for%20an%20error%20of%20judgement%20or%20a%20bona%20fide%20mistake%20while%20treating%20a%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%202005%20judgment%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20doctors%20from%20frivolous%20criminal%20prosecutions%20but%20emphasised%20accountability%20in%20cases%20of%20genuine%20medical%20negligence.%20The%20court%20laid%20down%20guidelines%20to%20differentiate%20between%20genuine%20errors%20and%20acts%20of%20negligence%20by%20medical%20practitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20points%20from%20the%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Gross%20Negligence%20Standard%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20held%20that%20for%20a%20doctor%20to%20be%20held%20criminally%20liable%2C%20the%20negligence%20should%20be%20of%20such%20a%20high%20degree%20as%20to%20amount%20to%20gross%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Intentional%20Acts%20or%20Omissions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20clarified%20that%20criminal%20liability%20would%20arise%20only%20if%20a%20medical%20professional%E2%80%99s%20act%20or%20omission%20is%20so%20reckless%20or%20negligent%20that%20it%20can%20be%20equated%20with%20a%20criminal%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Professional%20Standards%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20high%20professional%20standards%20and%20medical%20ethics%2C%20and%20that%20a%20breach%20of%20these%20standards%20could%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20criminal%20liability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Expert%20Opinion%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20highlighted%20the%20significance%20of%20obtaining%20expert%20opinion%20to%20establish%20negligence%2C%20and%20that%20the%20opinion%20should%20be%20given%20by%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20same%20field%20as%20the%20one%20being%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%20has%20since%20been%20cited%20in%20various%20judgements%20related%20to%20medical%20negligence%20in%20India%20and%20provided%20a%20framework%20for%20determining%20when%20criminal%20liability%20may%20be%20imposed%20on%20medical%20practitioners%20for%20their%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20it%20mean%20for%20patients%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Asokan%20added%20that%20there%20is%20always%20the%20possibility%20of%20seeking%20civil%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20negligence%2C%20which%20aligns%20with%20what%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Claw%20of%20thoughts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20medical%20profession%20falls%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20this%20law%20and%20while%20we%20adhere%20to%20it%2C%20our%20contention%20lies%20in%20distinguishing%20it%20from%20criminal%20negligence.%20In%20the%20realm%20of%20criminal%20law%2C%20intent%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%2C%20often%20denoted%20by%20the%20Latin%20term%20%E2%80%98mens%20rea%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20exists%20a%20distinction%20between%20a%20doctor-patient%20relationship%20and%20instances%20of%20medical%20negligence%20or%20accidents%2C%20such%20as%20unpredictable%20events%2C%20like%20anaesthetic%20deaths%2C%20which%20are%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20medical%20accidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20IMA%E2%80%99s%20stance%20emphasised%20that%20the%20medical%20profession%20complies%20with%20the%20law%20of%20civil%20compensation%20and%20the%20law%20of%20thoughts%2C%20but%20it%20rejects%20the%20notion%20of%20criminal%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20position%20has%20found%20support%20from%20the%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20On%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20expressed%20intention%20to%20amend%20the%20law%2C%20stating%20that%20in%20the%20context%20of%20treatment%2C%20there%20is%20no%20murder%20involved%2C%20and%20doctors%20can%20be%20exempted.%20This%20statement%20marks%20a%20departure%20from%20what%20the%20government%20had%20previously%20articulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20civil%20liabilities%2C%20the%20consumer%20commission%20is%20the%20available%20platform%20for%20patients%20who%20find%20doctors%20and%20hospitals%20liable%20for%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20hospitals%20and%20doctors%20are%20covered%20under%20indemnity%20insurance%2C%20a%20financial%20arrangement%20that%20provides%20protection%20against%20potential%20losses%20or%20damages%20by%20compensating%20doctors%20for%20covered%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Asokan%2C%20the%20new%20law%20is%20advantageous%20for%20both%20doctors%20and%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20loss%2C%20patients%E2%80%99%20families%20can%20pursue%20civil%20suits%20without%20doctors%20being%20perceived%20as%20criminals%20or%20murderers.%20This%20instils%20confidence%20in%20doctors%2C%20especially%20in%20critical%20situations%2C%20eliminating%20the%20fear%20of%20imprisonment%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20calculated%20risks.%20The%20beneficiaries%20here%20are%20both%20the%20patient%20and%20the%20doctor%2C%20making%20it%20a%20positive%20development%20for%20public%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Asokan%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2F%5C%22%3E%20South%20First%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Read%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fhealth%2Fima-hails-legal-safeguard-doctors-gratitude-as-new-legislation-curbs-criminal-prosecution-in-cases-of-medical-negligence%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703420441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F01124355%2FDYF-camp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-is-the-ima-cheering-if-doctors-are-